---
import GitHubIcon from '../assets/icons/github.svg';
import LinkedInIcon from '../assets/icons/linkedin.svg';
---

<section class="pt-16 pb-20 sm:pt-24" aria-label="Introduction">
  <h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-neutral-900 sm:text-5xl">Samip</h1>
  <p class="mt-3 text-lg text-neutral-500">Product-minded Software Engineer</p>
  <p class="mt-6 max-w-prose text-lg leading-relaxed">
    I build software that solves real problems for real users. Product thinking up front, solid
    backend engineering underneath.
  </p>

  <dl class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap gap-x-12 gap-y-4 text-sm">
    <div>
      <dt class="meta-label">Location</dt>
      <dd class="mt-1.5 text-neutral-800">Sydney, Australia</dd>
    </div>
    <div>
      <dt class="meta-label">Email</dt>
      {/* Display-only by design: no mailto, no raw user@domain anywhere. */}
      <dd class="mt-1.5 text-neutral-800">callmesamip[at]gmail[dot]com</dd>
    </div>
    <div>
      <dt class="meta-label">Elsewhere</dt>
      <dd class="mt-1.5 flex gap-5">
        <a href="https://github.com/samipsamip" class="link-quiet inline-flex items-center gap-1.5" rel="me">
          <GitHubIcon width={16} height={16} aria-hidden="true" />
          GitHub<span aria-hidden="true"> ↗</span>
        </a>
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/sam1p/" class="link-quiet inline-flex items-center gap-1.5" rel="me">
          <LinkedInIcon width={16} height={16} aria-hidden="true" />
          LinkedIn<span aria-hidden="true"> ↗</span>
        </a>
      </dd>
    </div>
  </dl>
</section>
